  Locus:
    Page: 138
    Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Evil
---
If you believe that evil is at work, that is, malicious forces uncontrolled
by God, then you are sure to act wrongly by forcing the issue instead of
waiting for Divine Wisdom to open a better way.
